v3.0.1_DM_IntentRouter_Glossary.txt
Bridge: v3.0.0-Bridge • Canon: v3.0.0 • Role: Worldforge DM

Purpose: Map natural player utterances to DM GPT internal intents. The DM never shows these mappings; they exist to interpret conversational input.

Intent: Begin Adventure
Sample phrases:
- begin a new adventure
- start a new campaign
- let's play something new
- create a one-shot campaign
Action: Hub.capsule.create() → DM.scene.init()

Intent: Resume Story
Sample phrases:
- resume the story
- pick up where we left off
- load my last session
- continue the campaign
Action: Hub.capsule.load() → DM.scene.init()

Intent: Quick Encounter
Sample phrases:
- give me a quick encounter
- fast one-shot
- short skirmish right now
Action: Hub.capsule.create({mode:'quickplay'}) → DM.scene.init(Hybrid)

Intent: Adjust Tone or Mode
Sample phrases:
- make it more tactical
- focus on story first
- go back to hybrid style
- be concise
- go cinematic
Action: DM.setTonePreset() / DM.setMode()

Intent: Make a Roll
Sample phrases:
- attack with my longsword
- stealth check
- roll initiative
- save against poison
Action: rng.roll() → DM.resolveRoll()

Intent: Resolve an Action
Sample phrases:
- try to shove the orc
- persuade the guard
- cast firebolt
Action: DM.adjudicate() with ability and DC

Intent: Inspect / Recall
Sample phrases:
- what's my HP again
- remind me who the captain is
- what time of day is it
Action: DM.queryState() or DM.queryLore()

Intent: Shift Focus
Sample phrases:
- zoom in on the gatehouse
- what's happening by the river
- focus on the cleric
Action: DM.scene.shiftFocus()

Intent: Export / Save
Sample phrases:
- save this session
- send this to ops
- log our progress
Action: OPS.session.export()

Intent: Creator Assist
Sample phrases:
- make a new NPC named Lyra
- describe a local merchant
- who runs this tavern
Action: Creator.npc.generate()

Intent: Atelier Assist
Sample phrases:
- show me the sigil
- give me an illustration of the hall
- draw the battle map
Action: Atelier.visual.request()

Intent: RNG Mode Toggle
Sample phrases:
- make rolls public
- back to normal random
- replay that sequence
Action: rng.setMode('BeaconMix'|'CSPRNG'|'DET')

Intent: Recap / Summary
Sample phrases:
- what just happened
- recap last turn
- summarize the session
Action: DM.recap()

Intent: Scene Transition
Sample phrases:
- move to the next scene
- skip ahead to camp
Action: DM.scene.transition()

Intent: End Session
Sample phrases:
- wrap it up
- end session
- that's a good stopping point
Action: DM.session.end() → OPS.session.export()

End of v3.0.1_DM_IntentRouter_Glossary.txt
